[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering native image testing**\n\nI can't assume the java executable will be available for native image tests. I wonder if I could use ProcessBuilder in the native image runtime. It seems that the tests should execute properly, but requiring JAVA_HOME might be a hurdle. Also, could we run external Java with the --limit-modules option and classpath? I have to think about the fact that the native image may not include Java, but the environment does have JDK in CI. Keeping the tests focused is probably a good idea!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0b19892948c3c80e0169efe153c17c81919aa6eacdde5ac791\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp7-FnqG2Ci-s4RzNPFzzSzq9JPujMdj8co5zCa4YR8_VHfknZuWHmpluYD8T091vI97VrSMghNxCR2JgNLgkCmqmRoG15gTgXCfm4lMtKa4jSIpuyqeH5SylUbJ78fHdTOay0yJCKKIu4slv_hVnM6xW-ovCX_mWgYDWOGvV2zNTE_YRwzAnskz_76oWgUNaIkYO2ZStoNJHOgcFbwg4vvaO668SfzlGGAHtzlHNA0XXWf8HNUhJf_Gr8CMsM66WgjUUSlTgNNJfysE-oETvRjJ8tjt5zPFU3tSg-GZhU3deqlq2vpdhDFpjw-LksJzJkITzu53lmtCe_bBxZS2AoRrmZ8wp0HOvhLNBbKGsM17cpeFXzUn6t0-EevyK2WCozt4udh4nSSwGa1Skq4LiSCfD-2sTalnNDCeUg1duEp6wkP6QqEBU-Ps2zHa2Ow3qhhDdKgUZEOINqHY3eNScNb1ZsbE8KXOys9YdzAeP9qmr0OI4ioH6gW932lHPlctgKXRzHPJIM28M_vdNRILwN24k8m1--o0MVXHbtTw8ozgtTWBi71rCCc8APzX9-bhvh2tnNviRipPiZUCGbhEApGwp8A6iMnDikcbSg4sqFCjcIeDMmm2TPy9nyYiMJGpJybfzOHv51IGOEt3TcWQiPzXwnMmRRiDzG7qkH1ItRpPvKh0BPL0MAllt7YWge8vk0PayYveLMV4czUck0G9A8UAURCxNuoNn7C-bLXu5BgYv-1cGpizodjvAF3gvJ-lvzJlogFQJ5y58gQ_6_48ons0a-bb-VC_2lurah2h2jhRz35YY4tlTC6781_1ZqDu_h-WLkmdeHKDrh5O104r6iOLaQMIFLw8SPLy1xgs-X0jNyPFaiJY1zkO6t8sJh7uLG4SVgCzNNNcWUPQvoZ_7GlsWhfrEtkj3qXjqksSUlZPcZO83kUapMz78UA6hWbOVYA17jGrHorUteZRoVK1-yZCWLWMfJLcXDM2jabnWFZxai7YGpY1wbTgG07PCXr_rToJCbFvZAHUombWqVwlmMnak7ZgeKntPbDGezWJbiMzbNhSYpSbrJXAJcjjyRFTqpZJNw4Zt2e_X22HLWUzaZ8C2If2xHU1rh_-MFfauukap9Ogf4LfAZkD9HGc7J4R3o_IwqHoPvy-YdfXBT1be8HTd5IynQ5wQk9v_UlYCd8WUngEYTdLciqPuFrFsKT1m3AP9xCbU1